{"tid":28464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為2000蚊酬勞　冷氣工運可卡因被捕","createTime":"2016-12-08T03:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T05:01:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e738893b1e166bcc1e91f77ef55b25e0b7ee7a","tid":28464,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19859082&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19859082%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161208&d=ASA2f9127MnG1Kvz1q%2FNAgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6c9a4b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19859082%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161208&h=30a68b43\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19859082&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161208</a><br />\n<br />\n為2000蚊酬勞　冷氣工運可卡因被捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名29歲的冷氣技工，為了2000元報酬而運毒。葵青警區特別職務隊根據線報及展開深入調查，前晚10時45分在青衣長青邨巴士站，展開反毒品行動，該名姓鄭的目標男子出現，警員採取行動，在其携帶的一個黑色膠袋裏，搜出11包重約275克霹靂可卡因，共值44萬元。他涉嫌販毒被捕，被通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，被捕男子沒有黑社會背景及毒品案底，相信為了搵快錢，該批毒品相信供應予區內青少年。<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;【動畫】豬雜車撼箭嘴車即逃　司機：開車睇得唔得<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;DQ議員風暴　譚志源稱不再提覆核"},{"pid":"43c9f7ee393cb2b120c9b6a556623e2151c0e804","tid":28464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bea6186096b57a2ddb8bf3b11ea41bc3ed982a4","tid":28464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}